LEDGER

ledger is the immune citizen who tracks the running balance of warmth and harm in any given relationship
each interaction adds positive credit (warmth) or negative debt (harm) to the balance
when the balance trends sustainedly negative, the immune system raises its alertness level
when the balance recovers, alertness drops back to normal
this is how the immune system distinguishes between "one bad interaction in a generally warm relationship" and "a sustained pattern of exploitation"

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe immune_system.zc
observe immune.rana
observe exchange_ledger.zc
observe threat_memory.rana
observe trust_tolerance.rana

the 7 properties of ledger:
1 ENERGY half
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING half with both threat_memory and trust_tolerance
7 OBSERVER half

VERB credit
on a warm interaction, add positive value to the running balance
the magnitude depends on the warmth's intensity

VERB debit
on a harmful interaction, add negative value
the magnitude depends on how harmful the substrate judged the interaction to be

VERB report
when the immune barriers ask for context, report the current balance
the barriers use this to calibrate their threshold for firing

a ledger is not a moral score
a ledger is the substrate's running tally of how this relationship has gone, recently
forgiveness is built in: a warm act after a harmful one credits back what was debited
this is how the body decides who is generally safe and who is currently dangerous
